&lt;p&gt;After clearing out &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;contents/*.md&lt;/code&gt; and other such unused things, I attempted to build and deploy with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;yarn run build:gh&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
